  <summary date="2018-11-02T19:00:02Z" status="Introduced in House">Online Credit Card Disclosure Act of 2018 

This bill amends the Truth in Lending Act to revise disclosure requirements for an open end consumer credit plan (credit card). Specifically, creditors must include repayment information applicable to the consumer's outstanding credit card balance on an online interface used to make a payment.</summary>
